# Code Review Findings

Status: ✅ Done / ❌ Open / ⏭ Skipped

## Bugs / Will Fail

1. **`build.sbt:41`** — `assembly / mainClass` — ✅ **False positive**. Was already `org.polyconf.argfmt.ArgFormatter` (correct).

2. **`CustomAccumulators.remove`** — ✅ **File removed** per review.

3. **`ParallelOps.parallelRun`** — ✅ **Fixed**. Now processes all inputs, collects failures, throws first at end.

## Dead / Unused Code

4. **`PolySerde.any2ConfNode`** — ✅ **Kept by request** — user wanted it restored after removal.

5. **`PolySerde.javaSerialize` / `javaDeserialize`** — ❌ Used only in one `SerdeSpec` test.

6. **`log4j.properties`** — ✅ **Removed** (log4j 1.x format, ignored by log4j 2.x).

7. **`ArgFormatterSpec.ArgFormatStub`** — ❌ Abstract class registered only to test `registerBase`. Could use existing `EscapeFormatBase`.

8. **`ParallelOps` import `scala.language.reflectiveCalls`** — ✅ **False positive**. Needed for structural type access on anonymous `AutoCloseable` with `threadPool` member.

9. **`CustomAccumulators`** — ✅ **File removed** (thin delegation wrapper, adds no value).

## Inconsistencies

10. **`DESCRIPTION.md`** — ✅ **Updated** to reflect current codebase.

11. **`RunnerStream.help`** — ✅ **False positive**. Style (`"""` + newline + `|` + `stripMargin`) is consistent with all other help strings.

12. **`TransformerData.mapData`** — ✅ **Fixed**. Removed no-op `fold`, now `copy(data = data.map(f))`.

13. **`CliRunParamsGenerator.toArgs`** — ✅ **Fixed**. `f"..."` → `s"..."`.

14. **`@transient lazy val Log` vs `private lazy val Log`** — ⏭ **Skipped** — cosmetic only.

15. **`final case class` vs `case class`** — ✅ **Fixed**. All case classes are now `final`.

## Design Concerns

16. **`PolyConf.addDeserializer`** creates new `ObjectMapper.copy()` on every `deserialize` — ⏭ **Skipped** — `ObjectMapper.copy()` is cheap.

17. **`PolySerde.jsonRecursiveMapper`** is a `def` — ❌ Creates new `ObjectMapper` + module each access.

18. **`FileSource` trait with concrete `val` defaults** — ❌ `val path: String = ""` silently masks missing config.

19. **`SimpleDataGenerator` / `SimpleDataWriter` / `VerifyDataWriter` case classes with empty constructors** — ❌ Jackson sets fields via FIELD access, but `equals`/`hashCode` ignore data fields.

20. **`RunnerStream` is a case class with mutable pipeline** — ❌ Case classes should be immutable.

## Documentation Drift

21. **`DESCRIPTION.md` Non-goals** — ✅ **Fixed** — no longer mentions those dependencies.

22. **No comment on log4j-1.2-api bridge** — ❌ `build.sbt:18` — included but undocumented. Needed for Hadoop transitive deps.

## Minor

23. **`PolyConfRegistry.resolveClass`** — ✅ **Simplified**. Removed redundant `Try`/`fold`.

24. **`.jvmopts` `-Xmx4G`** vs IntelliJ config `-Xmx8192m` — ❌ Minor inconsistency.

25. **`PolyUtil.waitedGet` / `waitForCondition`** — ✅ **Fixed**. Now throws actual failure cause instead of misleading `TimeoutException`; improved error message for retry-limit exhaustion.
